testing

Interface Tester

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AuthenticationTester, BandTester, EventTester, FinanceTester, MemberTester, PlaceTester

    public interface Tester
    testing-interfaces which all tester-classes implement; each tester-class runs the testcases to verify the use-cases of another class
    Author:
    OOP Gruppe 187

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void printTestDescription()
      return a description of all test cases
      void printTestResults()
      prints the number of failed/successful tests; if any tests have failed; it prints the description of these test cases
      void runTests()
      runs all test cases that were specified
